JAVA THREADS

--  Utilities in JAVA_HOME\bin: jstack, jps.
--  To get the process identifier (PID) of a java process:
    $ jps -mv
--  To a get a dump thread to a file:
    $ jstack -l <PID> > dump.txt   (where <PID> is obtained with jps)